{"tid":1463331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得民意冇用既人，希望你地入黎睇睇","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:03:53.000Z","uid":237080,"like":23,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"718392fe06f411c8854be96e17b8fff793d9b817","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:46:17.000Z","msg":"呢兩個幾月，我都曾經嬲到覺得民意唔重要 (wfc?),<br />\n亦都覺得民意係牽制唔到呢個政府。<br />\n<br />\n但呢幾日我冷靜落黎諗諗，今次既反送中會係香港史上好重要既事，更可能係中國既歷史大事，即係話，我地係身處係歷史洪流入面，想逆流而上既一班抗爭者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">向來能引導社會方向既（無論你想要港獨定真普選），一係你有權，一係你有勢。</span>咩係權？中共係權，錢係權。<span style=\"color: gold;\">咩係勢？民意多寡係勢。</span>無權者，即係我地，已經算係弱勢既一方。<span style=\"color: gold;\">連勢都冇既話，你覺得你仲有咩bargaining power?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要更多人去加入我地，黎壯大我地既力量。呢個先係民意既重要性。</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係話過火既事/影響市民既事唔可以做，但要睇準時機，較岩力度咁去做。梁天琦個句「唔好俾仇恨沖昏頭腦」，意思係，我地正在做緊一件有可能係歷史上既大事。正因為係咁，我地要做好自己既情緒管理，zoom out少少去客觀地分析同盤算整個大局。唔好因爲嬲/失望，而做出d衝動既行為以致恨錯難返。<br />\n<br />\n既然係咁，我地係咪需要聽更多人既意見，反思自己每一個決定，trial and error，凝聚更多智慧同力量去逆流而上？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我本人錫春袋都唔會同你地割，但我好希望大家可以成功。所以希望大家可以用智慧，去好好反思有咩係應該做，乜野未係時候做。</span>"},{"pid":"a1f0500e3db6b9f7917dfd5b82842dc0673b8fab","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"自推一下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919ac2eaa4dd44fadccca645ee98fbf374876eb9","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"自推兩下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01ed3d12f9fd18756bb1f5d351e7f08275fb94a","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:56:34.000Z","msg":"自推三下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b70dc86a89803847096b099bee6439fbad5b0e6","tid":1463331,"uid":229553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"[公投] 817機場or紅土?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463062\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463062</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">612 721 811</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WEc7HxV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWEc7HxV.jpg&h=bc18cb82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNxu1GJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNxu1GJ.jpg&h=64932c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVOuhe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVOuhe4.jpg&h=a6d636f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K4DKCUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK4DKCUD.jpg&h=ba6c99d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdde39e975f514907ef1977ef9853cbc77032127","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"自推四下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125fbeff72a8c4cf61df59a24097285fe7904731","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"我真係唔想又去到幾年後既下一次，大家先識得去反思 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358be9aa3369e9ca345b0d55de22f8b41937cc74","tid":1463331,"uid":258646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:53.000Z","msg":"民意對連登仔係冇用嘅，因為連登仔唔需要選票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6770fde92b28448c4eb70bc0fe44c7b2ee03ac2e","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"358be9aa3369e9ca345b0d55de22f8b41937cc74","tid":1463331,"uid":258646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:47:53.000Z","msg":"民意對連登仔係冇用嘅，因為連登仔唔需要選票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔需要選票，但抗爭運動需要人呀！大量既人呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cd1c94f018d38237e7ad7a8b4de94e723ea6a1","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:52:33.000Z","msg":"自推五下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔介意俾人過面皮厚，最介意運動失敗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a95cbd2964cd3eb3317cbf90c64ad2fb7b34ac9","tid":1463331,"uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"其實你想影響經濟叫大家撳錢好過塞機場<br />\n而撳錢要民意"},{"pid":"e5bf048f4ece54aca6072004a3c144c965044467","tid":1463331,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"唔理民意嗰啲就一定係獨裁"},{"pid":"6c21ccdea7006222c911749fcad0fee64b5bef47","tid":1463331,"uid":118767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:55:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d06344c04ff560f8281a550a590b82f9755ec1f0","tid":1463331,"uid":157891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:56:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cc0ad39ba06b15378607dcef1c1a0bfb171d365","tid":1463331,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，失民意呀失民意呀，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n你地真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效，而又乜人都阻唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港又唔係民主政府，會聽民意，<br />\n你仲想攬住民意過世?  <br />\n文宣到有700萬人同你一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫你打政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋靠民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n各有各做，核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"5a74e8b51fc6f70c15c7745480ab7fb792437caf","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"運動成功之後，我理得你同班港豬割蓆到變塵都冇所謂。但我地而家唔單止要對抗藍屍，對抗黑警，對抗林鄭，我地真正既對手係中共呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人連支手搶都冇，已經冇武力可以威脅到佢地嫁喇。如果我地連人數都冇埋，我地仲搵咩去抗爭呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知就算七百萬人企出黎都冇用，但我地係咪可以嘗試叫佢地唔好淨係企出黎，起碼嘗試push佢地去諗下計，集思廣益，用佢地中年人既人脈黎救救香港呀？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地變得連企出黎都唔願意，你仲點叫佢地幫手呀？你當搵人抬下物資都好丫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efa9a45912e7964d9b37173f8d10cc5822a08b9","tid":1463331,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"2df06cb6bf0f9bb40f41c6a35e4eeb054398a74a","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cc0ad39ba06b15378607dcef1c1a0bfb171d365","tid":1463331,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，失民意呀失民意呀，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n你地真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效，而又乜人都阻唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港又唔係民主政府，會聽民意，<br />\n你仲想攬住民意過世?  <br />\n文宣到有700萬人同你一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫你打政府?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋靠民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n各有各做，核彈都唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"而家有d事唔係威脅到政權，係威脅緊我地自己呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係損敵一百，自損八千呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa76d42f0721af56fdd0d65846164153a2cb54a","tid":1463331,"uid":237080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:08:27.000Z","msg":"好心痛係明明大家都好聰明，都係有腦有力既人。點解唔思考下點樣可以威脅政權同得民心一齊做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWhy not both? 兩樣野真係可以冇衝突嫁。我最怕係林鄭流晒馬尿想拉攏人心既時候，我地幫左佢順水推舟咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9e1cdd88a64531a8a5b1bd07cb98731c61110c","tid":1463331,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"9f3749d5ce082af5327bbf60be913a0f77d5bed9","tid":1463331,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:13:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇民意嘅勇武係真暴動，冇民意嘅政府係真暴政</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果冇民意支持呀，出街擺個路障黑警未到呀已經比街坊圍住鬧啦<br />\n就好似黑警咁，黃大仙捉個都搞到比幾百人圍<br />\n<br />\n民意其實同我哋做緊嘅嘢冇太大衝突<br />\n只要我哋繼續對準政權，我地唔需要事事睇住民意<br />\n民意都會繼續支持<br />\n<br />\n但唔係話民意唔重要<br />\n做嘢嘅時候如果可以盡量減少損害民意就盡量做"},{"pid":"be33b43b1dec2d05afdde0e2def7824b1508d534","tid":1463331,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"help pish"},{"pid":"228180236ee35e5065de8dc38b8626caff32b05b","tid":1463331,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a325652a05da1ce080baf97a5d9bb7473d33c78","tid":1463331,"uid":222451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"軍政府撚有民意咩<br />\n勝者為王, 香港主流只係一班騎牆派同埋順民<br />\n唔需要全世界都支持你先做得野, 我地要喚醒可以醒既人已經夠<br />\n最重要係邊個勝利邊個有權威班廢物就會收聱<br />\n完"},{"pid":"a02e06ca56a0c6b4418719daa16b6de644957cf2","tid":1463331,"uid":282845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"理性post推"}]}